==Strategy==
Tyras guards can hit up to 15, and though there are a few [[safespot]]s, their [[halberd]] can reach over most of them. [[Protect from Melee]] will prevent a Tyras guard from damaging the player; food is strongly advised if not using [[Prayer]].

[[Magic]] can be dangerous to use because most robes have low defence and there is a lack of safe spots, but it has proven to be effective. If using [[Ancient Magicks]], a player can attack with [[ice spells]] so the guard cannot move, which is highly effective because of his weakness to Magic, and binding the guard results in most if not all damage avoided during the fight.

Alternatively, a player with high melee stats (60+) along with modest equipment should be capable of defeating a guard close up.

